text: The 1925 Dallas municipal election was a mayoral and municipal election in Dallas. Louis Blaylock beat Marvin E. Martin, W.S. Brambett, and, M.A. Smith, his opponents, for the office of mayor. ==References== Category:Dallas Category:Dallas municipal elections Category:Government of Dallas Category:Mayoral elections in Dallas Category:1925 Texas elections Dallas
title: 1925 Dallas municipal election
